description:
[section] [row] [col animate="fadeInDown"] [gap height="60px"]

INDOOR PLANTS

[gap height="60px"]

LULLY & ROSE thoughtfully curated range of orchids and indoor plants are the perfect gift for our green lovers.

[gap height="15px"] [ux_text line_height="1"]

All our indoor plants are carefully selected personally by us, then potted into a white ceramic planter, finished with moss and trailing ribbon.

[gap height="60px"] [divider align="center" width="full" height="1px" color="black"] [gap height="60px"]

INDOOR PLANTS

[/col] [/row] [/section]
